{
  "stem": "4226.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those who were sick were carried off, because the infantry came-- or they were not infantry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were also in trucks, only not tank units.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First aid and Red Cross and doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went down to probably-- wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roughly between 35 and 40 kilo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we went to house to house to see where we can-- we enter a house which has no prisoners.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we found one place not only for prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Let's go in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're going in in the pajamas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German people, elderly people, they were scared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The prisoners escaped, and they're going to kill them or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they were patting us on the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come in the lunch room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had cakes and coffee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these four Yugoslavs were there with their feet up on the table [LAUGHS] having a coffee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they-- afterwards, there was real coffee they had, from bean coffee.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we never had coffee, good coffee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] Silberstein just said to me, I think this, this coffee must have been poisoned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It tasted funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He said-- it wasn't poisoned, just he didn't have real coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why would they poison you in the last day?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course it wasn't poisoned, because the Germans drink it, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we, we left the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went into the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We said-- we saw American military kitchens set up under canvas, no sides, only roof.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were ready for dinner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were cooking and calling us in, giving us cheese and whatever they had got.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Fried bread.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said to myself, now what, what we do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Said no, [INAUDIBLE] we're going to sleep in a barn.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
